data.description: Estate Sale.  A solid manufactured home on large lot. Three out buildings are included in the sale.  Some contents may be for sale also.  Administrator of the Estate is in the process of cleaning out the home so it is a bit cluttered.  Fully fenced.  The property is in Probate  so sale requires court approval and will be subject to an overbid.
